he intersection\nbetween geometry and algorithmic pricing areas. Thus its study may lead to new\nalgorithmic techniques that could benefit both areas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2012 20:36:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2012 09:13:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-25"}
